nGF56g/va3wS__jdjAHlCpiLu16KJkSliAj5mAB/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="玛格丽特·萨瑟林 |布隆伯格"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;— 玛格丽特·萨瑟林&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国和以色列周五轰炸了&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/a3ICsogyDviWTPjHg0qf40OSGIrJPYRwfZu6vXWC23axHu2bKIYKCM3qQSbe8h1KCRXk6EN5sFGumIC0oaY1_MagJFEk3gLMheCrxqlqYjwDRkAOaOfSSiw3Z9dGCg0nwRzhsh6C4tTvVcCWZuFolUirkVL8kro0QDl9q6g-zsnvsHoWsk_laMOtIUuCxapqA_YFyL-rWtHXw-8wJEIRh9bb9-JJql-SHxyzrkpKr47MejXfvanlARo3Lyttdaq2w0Tw8QNFHNi68K_FzFf5efyNNJCjrkD7AsVas7ciHmneoWXfRiWWv2esO2ICYCsrTg9H1CbIKI50yL9Nv_ZuArCxjurgUa3Kc8uQ8b-MCUQGbVZpZmSoTvAhxUFkvrcVNJ8to233Vfx9zoxBCMPAQM-y50GaEkUshb3YNTZnw03Xsz5MsXnEpL4jFtZIihY6rCPBjlwqv__iczHs77cVzo5RVphwDq2JF7ju8DWQ55pWJQBjWhfeU_uRp39arAOH5Blj9g/GspEUj8btcvEJpq-leHSIC8opYhNNBQ3/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美国和以色列袭击核目标，德黑兰誓言报复"&gt;伊朗核目标&lt;/a&gt;和钢铁设施，而伊朗在波斯湾周围发动了更多空袭，损坏了科威特的两个港口，并促使多哈发出导弹警报。这些袭击发生之前，特朗普推迟了伊朗同意重新开放霍尔木兹海峡的最后期限，否则其发电厂将面临袭击。这是他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/zfn4Oj55m57I7d7Rg_EEbRORpL64QtpC6f-I4oR3f5BvlWWxvTos-RndMI4nZW4sjLNXmRe3WE-d__A--ISa8JMit_YpaegyEelaWCmvNyP7HUDVhaxN5xugECKT87wAeFkQij2wNDIhxA8qcJOB1bgRJrjI6Uka8M75IeucsGMz7PJ2pdWC78oDSvNRvoeP8O4_JGhdDujPzME56XoK1t7_tkfwlFYKGUcuLiZ3A_DsGY9WY4IttAH_8dtZobcyuknOuCLMrF92IxSF-MO_bTWAsLCaSe5ydtGs8z4mCGPC2kVJN9mQDO2pAu1d22CFTqG8GLyQeem43Zly7hk/u0XAkd_aGlwtO__ap_u0ywQGYVALTc62/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="真相社会"&gt;自周六威胁&lt;/a&gt;如果德黑兰不重新开放关键水道就摧毁基础设施以来的第二次延期。随着全球能源和大宗商品短缺的加剧，这一阻塞点变得越来越紧迫。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;与此